body:
As if mages weren&#039;t disadvantaged enough by the new assassin update..

Now you take away the only item that mages could use to defend against assassins..

I know Rylai&#039;s is strong and probably in need of a nerf. But seriously? **100 HP 25 AP 20% slow, and 0.5 sec duration** IN ONE GO?

When you nerfed Zed you were like 
&quot;Ohhhhhhh, ahhhhhhh _[tentative flick]_ Whew! that little bit of dust has gone from him! Now... OH SHIT ADD IT BACK ON AGIAN! HE CANT 1v5 PENTA ANYMORE!!!! FUUUUUUUUUCK!&quot;

But when you nerf Rylai&#039;s &quot;_[Punch in the bollocks!]_ Pffffff! she&#039;ll be right mate!&quot;

Seriously??

In the same patch you are like &quot;Azir is weak atm, lets give him the slightest nudge, buuuut remove his core item. DW itll be fine!&quot;
